001p.pdf}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=parmasto1984>{{cite journal |last=Parmasto |first=E. |year=1984 |title= ''Cymatellopsis'', a new genus of reduced Tricholomataceae from East Asia|journal=Nova Hedwigia |volume=40 |issue=1\u20134 |pages=463\u2013468}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=Patouillard1889>{{cite journal |last=Patouillard |first=Narcisse Th\u00e9ophile |year=1889 |title=Fragments mycologiques. Notes sur quelques champignons de la Martinique |journal=Journal de Botanique (Morot) |volume=3 |pages=335\u201343 |language=French  |trans-title=Mycological fragments. Notes on a few Martinican fungi}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=Patouillard1899>{{cite journal |last=Patouillard |first=Narcisse Th\u00e9ophile |year=1889 |title=Champignons de la Guadeloupe |journal=Bulletin de la Soci\u00e9t\u00e9 Mycologique de France |volume=15 |pages=191\u2013209 |language=French |trans-title=Fungi of the Guadeloupe}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=patouillard1900>{{cite book |last=Patouillard |first=N. |year=1900 |title=Essai taxonomique sur les familles et les genres des Hym\u00e9nomyc\u00e8tes |publisher=Poisson |location=Lons-le-Saunier |page=146 |url=https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/page/28232960 |language=French |trans-title=Taxonomic essay on Hymenomycete families and Genera}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=petersen1999>{{cite journal |last=Petersen |first=Ronald H. |author2=Irmgard Krisai-Greilhuber  |year=1999 |title=Type specimen studies in ''Pleurotus'' |journal=Persoonia |volume=17 |issue=2 |pages=201\u2013219 |doi=}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=pilat1927>{{cite journal |last=Pil\u00e1t |first=Albert |year=1927 |title=''Skepperia carpatica'' sp. n., nouvelle esp\u00e8ce int\u00e9ressante du genre ''Skepperia'' Berk. dans les Carpathes centrales |trans-title=''Skepperia carpatica'' sp. nov., a new interesting species in ''Skepperia'' Berk. from Central Carpathian Mountains |journal=Bulletin trimestriel de la Soci\u00e9t\u00e9 mycologique de France |volume=43 |issue= |pages=49\u201358 |language=French}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=quelet