358 |language=French}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=quelet1884>{{cite book |last=Qu\u00e9let |first=Lucien |year=1884 |title=Enchiridion Fungorum in Europa media et praesertim in Gallia Vigentium |location=Paris |publisher=O.Doin |pages=216 |url=http://gallica.bnf.fr/ark:/12148/bpt6k441429c/f224 |language=Latin}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=reid1961>{{cite journal |last=Reid |first=Derek A. |year=1961 |title=Fungi Venezuelani V. The Cyphellaceae of Venezuela |journal=Kew Bulletin |volume=15 |issue=2 |pages=261\u2013275 |jstor=4109366 |doi=10.2307/4109366}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=reid1964>{{cite journal |last=Reid |first=Derek A. |year=1964 |title=Notes on some fungi of Michigan-I. Cyphellaceae |journal=Persoonia |volume=3 |issue=1 |pages=97\u2013154 |doi=}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=roussel1806>{{cite book |last=de Roussel |first=Henri Fran\u00e7ois Anne |year=1806 |title=Flore du Calvados et terrains adjacents, compos\u00e9e suivant la m\u00e9thode de Jussieu |edition=2nd |location=Caen |publisher=Poisson |page=62|language=French |trans-title=Flora of Calvados and adjacent areas, according to the method of Jussieu}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=singer1938-SZP>{{cite journal |last=Singer |first=Rolf |year=1938 |title=Phylogenie und Taxonomie der Agaricales |journal=Schweizerische Zeitschrift f\u00fcr Pilzkunde |volume=17 |issue= |pages=71\u201373 |doi=|language=German |trans-title=Phylogeny and taxonomy of the Agaricales}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=singer1938>{{cite journal |last=Singer |first=Rolf |year=1938 |title=Notes sur quelques Basidiomycetes |journal=Revue de Mycologie |volume=3 |pages=187\u2013199 |language=French |trans-title=Notes on a couple Basidiomycetes}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=singer1943>{{cite journal |last=Singer |first=Rolf |year=1943 |title=A monographic study of the genera ''Crinipellis'' and ''Chaetocalathus'' |journal=Lilloa |volume=8 |issue=3 |pages=441\u2013534}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=singer1944>{{cite journal |last=Singer |first=Rolf |year=1944 |title=New genera of fungi. I |journal=Mycologia 