ra|last=Somayaji|date=27 July 2015|work=Bloomberg L.P.|accessdate=27 November 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151227212649/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2015-07-27/teva-snaps-up-allergan-s-generics-arm-dumping-mylan|archive-date=27 December 2015|url-status=live}}</ref><ref group=\"N\">40.5 billion = $33.75 billion in cash + $6.75 billion worth of shares</ref>\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 34\n| 2018\n| {{flagicon|USA}} [[Comcast Corporation]]\n| {{flagicon|UK}} [[Sky plc]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|39.0\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|{{inflation|US|39|2018}}\n|<ref name=\"auto3\">{{cite web|url=https://uk.reuters.com/article/us-sky-m-a-fox/comcast-raises-bid-for-sky-to-34-billion-tops-foxs-offer-idUKKBN1K10KU|title=Comcast raises bid for Sky to $34 billion, tops Fox's offer|first=Paul|last=Sandle|access-date=2018-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180716223837/https://uk.reuters.com/article/us-sky-m-a-fox/comcast-raises-bid-for-sky-to-34-billion-tops-foxs-offer-idUKKBN1K10KU|archive-date=2018-07-16|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name=\"auto4\">{{cite web|url=https://uk.reuters.com/article/us-sky-m-a-auction/comcast-outbids-fox-with-39-billion-offer-for-sky-in-auction-idUKKCN1M20U2|title=Comcast outbids Fox with 30.6 billion pounds winning offer for Sky|first=Ben|last=Martin|access-date=2018-09-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180922194259/https://uk.reuters.com/article/us-sky-m-a-auction/comcast-outbids-fox-with-39-billion-offer-for-sky-in-auction-idUKKCN1M20U2|archive-date=2018-09-22|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>https://www.engadget.com/2018/09/22/comcast-to-acquire-sky/</ref>\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 35\n| 2018\n| {{flagicon|GER}} [[E.ON SE]]\n| {{flagicon|GER}} [[Innogy SE]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|38.5\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|{{inflation|US|38.5|2018}} \n|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://uk.reuters.com/article/us-deals-review/global-mergers-and-acquisitions-reach-record-high-in-fir