kxf9\">Raugust, Karen, (March 4, 2008) \"[http://vfxworld.com/?atype=articles&id=3568 ''Lost'': Season 4&nbsp;\u2013 VFX Interrupts]\", VFXWorld. Retrieved on March 19, 2008.</ref>\n<ref name=\"dboLH\">Sinclair, Lara, (February 14, 2008) \"[http://www.theaustralian.news.com.au/story/0,25197,23209038-26077,00.html ''Lost'' Fans Reunite in Drama Online] {{Webarchive|url=https://archive.is/20080217225645/http://www.theaustralian.news.com.au/story/0,25197,23209038-26077,00.html |date=2008-02-17}}\", ''[[The Australian]]''. Retrieved on March 17, 2008.</ref>\n<ref name=\"HNPF9\">Connelly, Michael Alan, (January 31, 2008) \"[https://nymag.com/daily/entertainment/2008/01/we_decode_the_lost_online_game.html ''Lost'' Billboard Purchaser Ordered 'Vandalism']\", ''[[List of newspapers in Iowa|Ames Tribune]]''. Retrieved on March 17, 2008.</ref>\n<ref name=\"K7yS2\">[[Bobby La Gesse|La Gesse, Bobby]], (January 9, 2008) \"[http://www.midiowanews.com/site/tab1.cfm?newsid=19182861&BRD=2700&PAG=461&dept_id=554432&rfi=6 We Decode the ''Lost'' Online Game for You] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080121020734/http://www.midiowanews.com/site/tab1.cfm?newsid=19182861&BRD=2700&PAG=461&dept_id=554432&rfi=6 |date=January 21, 2008}}\", ''[[New York (magazine)|New York]]''. Retrieved on March 17, 2008.</ref>\n<ref name=\"o71gv\">[[Damon Lindelof|Lindelof, Damon]] & [[Carlton Cuse|Cuse, Carlton]], (March 10, 2008) \"[http://ll.media.abc.com/podcast/audio/itunes/LOST_407_audio_podcast_2639b9f3-d701-4360-b0d4-ae298886bd2d_1591126.mp3 Official ''Lost'' Audio Podcast]\", [[American Broadcasting Company|ABC]]. Retrieved on March 1, 2008.</ref>\n<ref name=\"UqblE\">Jensen, Jeff \"Doc\", (February 20, 2008) \"[https://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20179125_4,00.html ''Lost'': Mind-Blowing Scoop]\", ''[[Entertainment Weekly]]''. Retrieved on March 17, 2008.</ref>\n<ref name=\"0gNqc\">[[American Broadcasting Company|ABC]] Medianet, (February 12, 2008) \"[http://abcmedianet.com/web/dnr/dispD