a]]\n| align=\"right\"| 46\n| align=\"right\"|   15,324\n| align=\"right\"| 4,000\n|-\n| align=\"left\"|[[Surangi]]\n| align=\"right\"| 14.75\n| align=\"right\"|  12,919\n| align=\"right\"| 3,500\n|-\n| align=\"left\"|[[Talasamudram]]\n| align=\"right\"| 1.37\n| align=\"right\"|  923\n| align=\"right\"| 2,383\n|-\n| align=\"left\"|Takkali Estates\n| align=\"right\"| 61.56\n| align=\"right\"|  58,054\n| align=\"right\"| 49,088\n|-\n| align=\"left\"|[[Tallavalasa]]\n| align=\"right\"| 0.37\n| align=\"right\"|  387\n| align=\"right\"| 424\n|-\n| align=\"left\"|[[Tarla]]\n| align=\"right\"| 28.75\n| align=\"right\"|  24,639\n| align=\"right\"| 4,000\n|-\n| align=\"left\"|[[Tarlepatta]]\n| align=\"right\"|0.75\n| align=\"right\"|    388\n| align=\"right\"| 256\n|-\n| align=\"left\"|[[Tilaru]]\n| align=\"right\"|15.75\n| align=\"right\"|   6,180\n| align=\"right\"| 3,654\n|-\n| align=\"left\"|[[Towdam]]\n| align=\"right\"| 2.5\n| align=\"right\"|  1,030\n| align=\"right\"| 686\n|-\n| align=\"left\"|[[Urlam]]\n| align=\"right\"|14.5\n| align=\"right\"|   11,061\n| align=\"right\"| 13,582\n|-\n| align=\"left\"|[[Yellamanchilli]]\n| align=\"right\"|1\n| align=\"right\"|   643\n| align=\"right\"| 654\n|-\n! style=\"background-color:#99ccff\" colspan=\"4\" align=\"left\"|Godavary district\n|-\n| align=\"left\"|Bhadrachalam and Rakapalli\n| align=\"right\"|505\n| align=\"right\"|  27,695\n| align=\"right\"|    21,090\n|-\n| align=\"left\"|Cocanada and Coringa\n| align=\"right\"|  168\n| align=\"right\"| 91,860\n| align=\"right\"|  -\n|-\n| align=\"left\"|[[Markundapadu]]\n| align=\"right\"|150\n| align=\"right\"|  5,500\n| align=\"right\"|   15,000\n|-\n| align=\"left\"|[[Pittapore]]\n| align=\"right\"| 188\n| align=\"right\"|   79,606\n| align=\"right\"|    3,41,627<ref>The rent for Pittapoor also included the rent for Cocanada and Coringa</ref>\n|-\n| align=\"left\"|[[Polavaram estate|Polavaram]]\n| align=\"right\"| 292\n| align=\"right\"|   58,274<ref>[https://books.google.c