aulofc.net/equipe/elenco/goleiros/rogerio-ceni/ S\u00e3o Paulo official profile] {{in lang|pt}}\n*{{Official website|http://www.rogerioceni.com.br/}} {{in lang|pt}}\n*{{NFT player|pid=1010}}\n*[http://www.iffhs.de/?b4a390f03be4ac07cda15b45fdcdc3bfcdc0aec70aee0a IFFHS Top Division goal scorer ranking among goalkeepers]\n\n{{Fortaleza Esporte Clube squad}}\n{{Campeonato Brasileiro S\u00e9rie A managers}}\n{{Navboxes\n| title = Brazil squads\n| bg          = #FFDF00\n| fg          = #008000\n| bordercolor = blue\n| list1 =\n{{Brazil squad 1997 FIFA Confederations Cup}}\n{{Brazil squad 2002 FIFA World Cup}}\n{{Brazil squad 2006 FIFA World Cup}}\n}}\n{{Navboxes colour\n| title = Awards\n| bg    = gold\n| fg    = navy\n| list1 =\n{{FIFA Club World Cup Golden Ball}}\n{{Bola de Ouro}}\n{{Craque do Brasileir\u00e3o}}\n{{2000 Bola de Prata}}\n{{2003 Bola de Prata}}\n{{2004 Bola de Prata}}\n{{2006 Bola de Prata}}\n{{2006 Campeonato Brasileiro S\u00e9rie A Team of the Year}}\n{{2007 Bola de Prata}}\n{{2007 Campeonato Brasileiro S\u00e9rie A Team of the Year}}\n{{2008 Bola de Prata}}\n{{Copa do Nordeste winning managers}}\n}}\n{{Navboxes\n| title = Rog\u00e9rio Ceni managerial positions\n| list1 =\n{{S\u00e3o Paulo FC managers}}\n{{Fortaleza Esporte Clube managers}}\n{{Cruzeiro Esporte Clube managers}}\n}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Ceni, Rogerio}}\n[[Category:1973 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:People from Pato Branco]]\n[[Category:Brazilian footballers]]\n[[Category:Association football goalkeepers]]\n[[Category:Sinop Futebol Clube players]]\n[[Category:S\u00e3o Paulo FC players]]\n[[Category:Campeonato Brasileiro S\u00e9rie A players]]\n[[Category:Association football goalkeepers who have scored]]\n[[Category:Brazil international footballers]]\n[[Category:1997 FIFA Confederations Cup players]]\n[[Category:2002 FIFA World Cup players]]\n[[Category:2006 FIFA World Cup players]]\n[[Category:FIFA Confederations Cup-winning players]]\n[[Category:FIFA World Cup-winning play